{"text_id":168506,"tokens":["This"," work"," investigates"," the"," theoretical"," status"," of"," $","B","_","s","$-","mixing"," and"," the"," lifetimes"," of"," heavy"," had","rons","."," The"," interplay"," of"," quantum"," chrom","odynamics"," and"," strong"," and"," weak"," interactions"," governs"," these"," quantities",","," leading"," to"," complex"," theoretical"," challenges","."," We"," explore"," existing"," theoretical"," frameworks"," and"," highlight"," their"," limitations"," in"," describing"," the"," rich"," phenomen","ology"," of"," heavy"," had","rons","."," Our"," analysis"," reveals"," significant"," discrepancies"," between"," current"," theoretical"," predictions"," and"," experimental"," measurements","."," We"," suggest"," possible"," reasons"," for"," these"," discrepancies",","," including"," the"," need"," for"," a"," more"," sophisticated"," treatment"," of"," non","-","perturb","ative"," effects","."," Furthermore",","," we"," discuss"," the"," role"," of"," $","B","_","s","$-","mixing"," in"," resolving"," certain"," long","-","standing"," puzzles"," related"," to"," heavy"," hadron"," lifetimes","."," Our"," findings"," motivate"," further"," theoretical"," and"," experimental"," efforts"," towards"," a"," deeper"," understanding"," of"," the"," fundamental"," interactions"," responsible"," for"," the"," observed"," patterns"," of"," heavy"," hadron"," decays","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}